'''[[Major General]] Mohamed Zahir''' ([[Dhivehi language|Dhivehi]]: މުހައްމަދު ޒާހިރު) is a former [[Chief of Defence Force (Maldives)|Chief of Defence Force]] of the [[Maldives National Defence Force]] of the [[Republic of Maldives]]. 

